rows.label: tlk42100121_03_msg0001
rows.name:
As someone who loves high places, Takaka really
wants to try climbing to the top of the World Tree, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
It stretches all the way up into the sky, so Takaka
has no idea how high it is, but... mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_03_msg0003
rows.name:
The view from the top must surely be
like something out of a dream, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Takaka's dream is to climb to the top of the World Tree
and raise a toast with Gulan Honeytea, mo!
